{"tid":51303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳2歲童吃瓜子鯁喉窒息亡","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T10:26:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3172bf9d3d98afd58031ba1be5e5191833cb7f12","tid":51303,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161223/s00004/1482459054137SL4_C59D3BA3E818AE0C662FC192BAC6B2B1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161223%2Fs00004%2F1482459054137SL4_C59D3BA3E818AE0C662FC192BAC6B2B1.jpg&h=6b0c5efa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n還有差不多一個月就到農曆新年，瓜子是少不了的賀年食物，但深圳昨午卻發生瓜子鯁死人悲劇，一名2歲男童吃瓜子時卡住氣管，雖即時送院搶救，惜最終不治。聖誕、新年和春節接連而來，不少乾果類或啫喱類食物都受到小朋友喜愛，家長要特別注意。 <br />\n<br />\n據內地《南方都市報》報道，事發昨天中午12時許，隨媽媽由安徽到深圳探親的2歲男童在親友家中吃瓜子，不料卻鯁住，透不過氣來。男童媽媽宋女士馬上叫車把兒子送到深圳仁愛醫院搶救，據男童姨婆稱，大約12時13、14分就開始搶救，其後轉送深圳市婦幼保健院，但男童最終不治。男童是家中唯一孩子，宋女士得知兒子猝逝，悲慟得當場暈倒，而男孩的爸爸則從安徽趕往深圳。 <br />\n<br />\n深圳仁愛醫院醫務部吳主任表示，男童送到醫院是12時15分左右，院方為男童做心肺復蘇，氣管插管發現男童氣管內有瓜子仁和米飯，「送來的時候心電圖是一條直線，搶救到1點01分，心電圖還是一條直線」。該院院楊院長則稱，異物誤入氣管，氣管有一個排異功能，會有神經反射，就會嗆咳和嘔吐，而誤咽會加重氣道阻塞。 <br />\n<br />\n小童吃東西鯁塞意外經常發生，雖然因此奪命的事故不多，但佳節當前，家長仍應小心一些「高危」食物，除了事件中與瓜子同類的乾果，還有如有核的水果、可變形的蒟蒻啫喱、橡皮糖、軟糖、黏性強的湯圓年糕等等。萬一不幸發生食物卡喉，應盡快送院急救，以免因氣管堵塞而致窒息、大腦缺氧，造成不能彌補的傷害。 <br />\n<br />\n(綜合)"},{"pid":"5f6a447858857abd4c2c01b04a1a5b2c714f3aa8","tid":51303,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f07c2fc6ac71975f14ce757e314a13da2b21d2d","tid":51303,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"訓練強國人民體格"},{"pid":"27be650fdce0472ed8d70b30efb93f22808becf4","tid":51303,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J07d1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ07d1x.jpg&h=67e2ce72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3b444cef049b1a6edc2e06aa865bb905ab8fbd7","tid":51303,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:27:38.000Z","msg":"食瓜子搞到老母瓜左個仔 幾邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fdf23b2781029caac715fbc0826a24c46cdcb4","tid":51303,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"苦根<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f3f9e0512303a3378285b1ee3de03102f208a4","tid":51303,"uid":25514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"點解中國d細路成日花式死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfb3ec99a8ba63eaa9b00f4188330c36f9113f5","tid":51303,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解中國d細路成日<span style=\"color: red;\">花式死亡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e406f23fffe8129a05543b1c9bd5e7ce3a301501","tid":51303,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:54:04.000Z","msg":"真係瓜子囉依鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2cffc91c42159160ed1f3014027e51f18220e0","tid":51303,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b812eaf6107dc6ea5a6c3ded79c3d9270737e5a4","tid":51303,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祝小朋友下世都做中國人向佢地報仇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}